    "/v2/courses/{course_uuid}/enrollments": {
      "get": {
        "tags": [
          "Courses"
        ],
        "summary": "List enrollments for a course",
        "description": "Returns a list of enrollments for a specific course.\n\n**filters:**\n`groups_uuid` - people's groups *(array of uuids)*\n`enrolled_at` - people's enrollment date *(datetime)*\n`last_active_on` - people's date of last activity in course *(datetime)*\n`progress` - people's progress in course *(number)*\n\n**default sorting:** `enrolled_at` DESC\n",
